<div id="review_623017570" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/623017570" />
    <a title="Jean-Paul Adriaansen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4239273-jean-paul-adriaansen"><img alt="Jean-Paul Adriaansen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1283706477p2/4239273.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/623017570?book_show_action=true">May 23, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jean-Paul Adriaansen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jean-Paul Adriaansen" href="/user/show/4239273-jean-paul-adriaansen">Jean-Paul Adriaansen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer623017570" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9924331930488210174">The story starts when impoverished Jim, used to a life in luxury, is 75 years old and living with a young Israeli woman. He assigns a nameless friend to write his biography. <br/>Jumping up and down in time, the narrator brings the story of the rising and falling of Jim&apos;s business empires and the stories of those who shared his life.<br/>This is a tale about closing deals, be it business or emotional deals. Ethics and morals can be overrun, for the deal has to be closed.<br/>A captivating novel that will stick</span>
  <span id="freeText9924331930488210174" style="display:none">The story starts when impoverished Jim, used to a life in luxury, is 75 years old and living with a young Israeli woman. He assigns a nameless friend to write his biography. <br />Jumping up and down in time, the narrator brings the story of the rising and falling of Jim's business empires and the stories of those who shared his life.<br />This is a tale about closing deals, be it business or emotional deals. Ethics and morals can be overrun, for the deal has to be closed.<br />A captivating novel that will stick with you for a long time.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="9924331930488210174" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


