<span id="freeTextContainer14119877416958948775">The first ten pages or so drew me in to waste my time. Boring. I skimmed 298 out of 398n pages and gave up. It&apos;s all narration. No suspense or intrigue. Basically it&apos;s an auto biography of as man who is a scammer, adventurer, liar, and womanizer seen through the eyes of his friend. Could&apos;ve been a much better book. </span>
  <span id="freeText14119877416958948775" style="display:none">The first ten pages or so drew me in to waste my time. Boring. I skimmed 298 out of 398n pages and gave up. It's all narration. No suspense or intrigue. Basically it's an auto biography of as man who is a scammer, adventurer, liar, and womanizer seen through the eyes of his friend. Could've been a much better book. </span>
